WEBVTT

00:03.006 --> 00:04.781
You know what makes me really mad?

00:04.962 --> 00:07.424
Racism? Classism?

00:07.740 --> 00:09.290
I don't know any more isms.

00:09.609 --> 00:11.425
I didn't get the promotion.

00:11.742 --> 00:15.162
They gave it to a guy, of course,
who's been there half the time I have.

00:15.214 --> 00:17.680
I bet he's only half as qualified too.

00:17.681 --> 00:19.437
That's sexism. (Gasps)

00:19.512 --> 00:21.051
Another ism.

00:21.387 --> 00:22.987
Gabi, I'm really upset.

00:23.299 --> 00:25.687
Sofia, if you feel that way
then you should just quit.

00:25.892 --> 00:28.418
- I did.
- What?

00:29.762 --> 00:31.406
How are we gonna pay our bills?

00:31.407 --> 00:32.759
How are we gonna pay our rent?

00:32.761 --> 00:34.610
Hey, how about a little
support for the girl

00:34.611 --> 00:36.649
who floated your rent when
you were in Switzerland?

00:36.650 --> 00:39.085
Or who gave up cable so that
you could have chef's knives?

00:39.086 --> 00:42.244
And who really needs a hug
and a roll of cookie dough.

00:42.297 --> 00:45.013
Oh, okay. No, you know what? You're right.

00:45.014 --> 00:46.443
It's gonna be fine.

00:46.938 --> 00:49.302
Yeah, you quit your job.

00:49.699 --> 00:51.448
<i>(Theme music playing)</i>

00:55.762 --> 00:57.936
<i>♪ She's in the spotlight ♪</i>

00:57.937 --> 00:59.755
<i>♪ and she turned my head ♪</i>

00:59.756 --> 01:01.693
<i>♪ she'd run a red light ♪</i>

01:01.694 --> 01:03.612
<i>♪ cos she's bad like that ♪</i>

01:03.613 --> 01:07.374
<i>♪ I like that ooh, baby, ooh, baby, baby ♪</i>

01:07.375 --> 01:10.562
